getStrategiesValue().notice: Returns usd value of the token balances and their sum in the strategies.All returned amounts have `UNIFORM_DECIMALS` decimals.

getStrategyDepositToken(uint256).notice: Returns deposit token of the strategy.

rebalanceBatch().notice: Rebalance batch, so that token balances will match strategies weight.

rebalanceStrategies().notice: Rebalance strategies, so that their balances will match their weights.

redeemReceiptsToShares(uint256[]).notice: Convert receipts into share tokens.Cycle noted in receipt should be closed.

redeemReceiptsToSharesByModerators(uint2.notice: Reedem shares for receipts on behalf of their owners.Cycle noted in receipts should be closed.Only callable by moderators.

removeStrategy(uint256).notice: Remove strategy and deposit its balance in other strategies.Will revert when there is only 1 strategy left.

setCycleDuration(uint256).notice: Minimum time needed to be able to close the cycle.

setFeesCollectionAddress(address).notice: Set address for fees collected by protocol.

setFeesPercent(uint256).notice: Set percent to take from harvested rewards as protocol fee.

setMinDepositUsd(uint256).notice: Minimum to be deposited in the batch.

setMinUsdPerCycle(uint256).notice: Minimum usd needed to be able to close the cycle.

setSupportedToken(address,bool).notice: Set token as supported for user deposit and withdraw.

supportsToken(address).notice: Returns whether this token is supported.

withdrawFromBatch(uint256[]).notice: Withdraw tokens from batch.Receipts are burned and user receives amount of tokens that was noted.Cycle noted in receipts should be current cycle.

withdrawFromStrategies(uint256[],address.notice: Withdraw tokens from strategies.On partial withdraw leftover shares transferred to user.If not enough shares unlocked from receipt, or no receipts are passed, then shares will be taken from user.Receipts are burned.Cycle noted in receipts should be closed.
